title: What Medicare beneficiaries need to consider during open enrollment
summary: Medicare open enrollment, which lasts until Dec. 7, gives beneficiaries the ability to select health coverage for 2026. Here's what experts recommend considering.

title: ACA enhanced subsidy lapse could hit early retirees hardest amid shutdown fight
summary: Older adults who aren't yet eligible for Medicare face the largest increases in health insurance premiums if enhanced ACA subsidies disappear.
